    "When <span class=\"person\">Moses</span> saw it, he wondered at the sight: and as he drew near to behold it, the voice of the LORD came unto him,",
    "Saying, I am the God of thy fathers, the God of <span class=\"person\">Abraham</span>, and the God of <span class=\"person\">Isaac</span>, and the God of <span class=\"person\">Jacob</span>. Then <span class=\"person\">Moses</span> trembled, and durst not behold.",
    "Then said the Lord to him, Put off thy shoes from thy feet: for the place where thou standest is holy ground.",
