    "And <span class=\"person\">Saul</span> was consenting unto his death. And at that time there was a great persecution against the church which was at <span class=\"place\">Jerusalem</span>; and they were all scattered abroad throughout the regions of <span class=\"place\">Judæa</span> and <span class=\"place\">Samaria</span>, except the apostles.",
    "And devout men carried Stephen to his burial, and made great lamentation over him.",
