    "And he arose and went: and, behold, a man of <span class=\"place\">Ethiopia</span>, an eunuch of great authority under Candace queen of the Ethiopians, who had the charge of all her treasure, and had come to <span class=\"place\">Jerusalem</span> for to worship,",
