    "And the Lord said unto him, <span class=\"word\">Arise, and go into the street which is called Straight, and enquire in the house of <span class=\"person\">Judas</span> for one called <span class=\"person\">Saul</span>, of Tarsus: for, behold, he prayeth,</span> ",
