    "And Ananias went his way, and entered into the house; and putting his hands on him said, Brother <span class=\"person\">Saul</span>, the Lord, even <span class=\"person\">Jesus</span>, that appeared unto thee in the way as thou camest, hath sent me, that thou mightest receive thy sight, and be filled with the Holy Ghost.",
    "And immediately there fell from his eyes as it had been scales: and he received sight forthwith, and arose, and was baptized.",
    "And when he had received meat, he was strengthened. Then was <span class=\"person\">Saul</span> certain days with the disciples which were at <span class=\"place\">Damascus</span>.",
