    "But <span class=\"person\">Saul</span> increased the more in strength, and confounded the Jews which dwelt at <span class=\"place\">Damascus</span>, proving that this is very <span class=\"person\">Christ</span>.",
    "And after that many days were fulfilled, the Jews took counsel to kill him:",
